---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <h1>About Our Company</h1>
  
  <section class="mission">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We strive to provide innovative solutions that empower businesses and individuals across various industries, driving growth and positive change in the world.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section class="values">
    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Innovation: We constantly push the boundaries of what's possible.</li>
      <li>Integrity: We conduct our business with honesty and transparency.</li>
      <li>Collaboration: We believe in the power of teamwork and partnerships.</li>
      <li>Excellence: We are committed to delivering high-quality solutions and services.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  
  <section class="team">
    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <p>Our diverse team of experts brings together a wealth of knowledge and experience from various fields. We're passionate about solving complex problems and creating value for our clients.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section class="contact">
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a question about our services or want to explore how we can work together, don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta-button">Contact Us</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #007bff;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #333;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #0056b3;
  }
</style>